OL,5,G2315 TikTok: Murder Gone Viral
OL,6,     FA look at the case of 17-year-old
OL,7,     FCharlie Cosser, who was fatally
OL,8,     Fstabbed by 16-year-old Yura
OL,9,     FVarybrus at an end-of-term summer
OL,10,     Fparty for teenagers. Charlie's dad
OL,11,     FMartin made his dying son a
OL,12,     Fpromise that he would campaign for
OL,13,     Fjustice and awareness of knife
OL,14,     Fcrime, and his TikTok videos tell
OL,15,     Fthe story of a family struggling
OL,16,     Fto come to terms with an act of
OL,17,     Fsenseless violence that tore their
OL,18,     Flives apart
